Package: step-certctl
Version: 0.1.9
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: step-cli, systemd, openssl, curl
Maintainer: Mohamed Reda Elkhadiri <mohamed@elkhadiri.com>
Description: Generic certificate renewal manager for Smallstep CA
 step-certctl provides a simple, config-driven approach to managing
 TLS certificates issued by Smallstep CA.
 .
 Features:
  - Config-driven certificate issuance and renewal
  - Systemd timer-based automatic renewal
  - Support for multiple certificates per host
  - Automatic service reloading after renewal
  - Serial number comparison to avoid unnecessary reloads
 .
 Ideal for managing certificates across Proxmox nodes, nginx servers,
 custom applications, and other infrastructure components.
